<div class="content">
  <h2 class="text-center">A community for petites, by petites!</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-2">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8 text-justify">
      <p>
        This is a place where we can help each other find things that fit and that make our lives a little easier.
      </p>
      <p>
      If you can relate to any of the following, you're in the right place!
        <ul>
          <li>
            Pants that are way too long. Capris look like high waters on you. Sleeves that go halfway down your hands.
          </li>
          <li>
            Not being able to see around other people, especially at shows or festivals.
          </li>
          <li>
            Your feet not touching the ground when you sit down. Whether that's at a restaurant, at work, on an airplane.
          </li>
          <li>
            At a loss when you're on a step stool and still can't reach something. Then climbing the counter and still not being able to reach.
          </li>
          <li>
            Trying to drive into the sun. Why does the sun visor extend horizontally, but not vertically?
          </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <p>
        The community needs your help to grow. To start contributing, please <%= link_to 'sign up', new_user_registration_path %>.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2">
    </div>
  </div><br><br> 
</div>
